<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Truth Archive</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
  background: #0a0a0a;
  color: white;
}

/* HERO */
.hero {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 120px 20px 80px;
}

h1 {
  font-size: 52px;
  margin: 0;
  color: #00ff88;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
}

.subtitle {
  color: #aaa;
  font-size: 18px;
  margin-top: 15px;
}

/* BUTTON */
.button {
  margin-top: 30px;
  display: inline-block;
  padding: 12px 24px;
  border: 1px solid #00ff88;
  color: #00ff88;
  text-decoration: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

.button:hover {
  background: #00ff88;
  color: black;
}

/* SECTIONS */
.section {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: auto;
  padding: 60px 20px;
}

.card {
  background: #111;
  border: 1px solid #1f1f1f;
  padding: 20px;
  border-radius: 12px;
  margin-top: 15px;
}

.card h3 {
  color: #00ff88;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 40px;
  color: #555;
  font-size: 14px;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="hero">
  <h1>TRUTH ARCHIVE</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Exploring Biblical truth, evidence, and reason in a modern world.</p>
  <a class="button" href="#start">Enter</a>
</div>

<div class="section" id="start">

  <h2 style="color:#00ff88;">Core Topics</h2>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Evidence for God</h3>
    <p>Philosophy, science, and historical arguments supporting the existence of God.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Biblical Reliability</h3>
    <p>Why the Bible stands as a historically and textually reliable document.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h3>Faith & Reason</h3>
    <p>Understanding how logic and faith work together, not against each other.</p>
  </div>

</div>

<footer>
  Built to seek truth — not opinion.
</footer>

</body>
</html>
